CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 16, 1954, pg. 6, reads: "Carver Luncheon - The tenth annual observance of George Washington Carver Week was highlighted with a luncheon at the Sheraton Hotel on Wednesday..."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing dark satin strapless gown and dark heels with ankle straps, singing on stage, woman on right playing piano, in Penn Sheraton Hotel for George Washington Carver luncheon
